summary: Animated loading screen replacer for Skyrim. (NSFW)
descriptionHtml:
[color=#CCFB5D][size=6][center]INFO:[/center][/size][/color][center][size=4]Replaces Skyrim loading screen with an animated clip.
[/size][/center][center][size=4]-The usual 3D model and game tips will not load so it helps with load times.[/size][/center]
[center][img]https://i.imgur.com/WA1JrDW.gif[/img]

[size=4][size=4]I made some NSFW main menus and someone suggested if I can make a loading screen too, so I made it.
Its mainly a test so maybe eventually I will make more or some "SFW" ones.[/size]
[size=4]I hope you like it. ;)[/size]
